  <h2 id="opportunity-attributes-2" class="govuk-heading-m app-summary-list-heading">About the work</h2>
  
  

  

  

  
<dl class="govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list--top-border govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Early market engagement
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Who the specialist will work with
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Will be reporting to Head of Engineering and working with Top Tier suppliers and internal project manager
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          What the specialist will work on
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          •	Managing a team of engineers<br>•	Managing integration build and integration testing<br>•	Assist in embedding a DevOps culture in the organisation<br>•	Follow and document good development standards and processes<br>•	Manage DevOps tools such as code repositories and monitoring<br>•	Setup and maintaining environments<br>•	Automation: Building CI/CD pipelines and test automation<br>•	Support of user requests<br>•	Patching and updating systems<br>•	Transform technical requirements into DevOps processes<br>•	Build complex stories without additional support<br>•	Manage live test environments<br>•	Identify and resolve issues preventing delivery<br>•	Produce systems design<br>•	Be user focus
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
</dl>

