  <h2 id="opportunity-attributes-6" class="govuk-heading-m app-summary-list-heading">How suppliers will be evaluated</h2>
  
  <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3">All suppliers will be asked to provide a work history.</p>
  
  

  

  

  

  
<dl class="govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list--top-border govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          How many specialists to evaluate
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          3
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Cultural fit criteria
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>be inclusive</li>
          <li>collaborative</li>
          <li>comfortable to ask questions</li>
          <li>Being truthful and open</li>
          <li>Creative self-starter</li>
          <li>solution focused</li>
          <li>able to demonstrate initiative</li>
          <li>effectively deal with requirements ambiguity</li>
          <li>develop pragmatic software solutions that realise business benefits</li>
        </ul>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Additional assessment methods
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>Reference</li>
          <li>Interview</li>
          <li>Scenario or test</li>
        </ul>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Evaluation weighting
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-0 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Technical competence</p>
        <div>50%</div>
        <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Cultural fit</p>
        <div>20%</div>
        <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Price</p>
        <div>30%</div>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
</dl>

  </div>
</div>
<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-full">
    

<h2 id="clarification-questions" class="govuk-heading-m app-summary-list-heading">Questions asked by suppliers</h2>



  

  

  

  

  

  
<dl class="govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list--top-border govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          1. 27 essential and nice-to-have skills will require a response in the region of 2,700 words in order to apply. From experience, this will deter the best talent available from applying – is there any way this can be shortened ?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Some of these requirements can be grouped together to reduce the number of requirements. To make it easier for searching, we explicitly broke them down to individual pieces. For example, ELK was expanded to the following 3. Elastic Search, Log Stash and Kibana.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          2. Please can you confirm the level of clearance required?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          BPSS is the minimum requirement. MHRA will also carry out additional checks.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          3. Is there a current or preferred incumbent for this? If there is any then please let us know what are the key pain points?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          No. N/A.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          4. Will you also consider SC eligible candidates and sponsor SC and DV for a candidate?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          The MHRA expect BPSS check to be completed before the start date and that this responsibility falls to the party representing the candidate
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          5. Is this requirement inside or outside of IR35?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Inside IR35
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          6. The candidate is willing to go through Security clearance. Would the SC clearance be sponsored?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          The MHRA expect BPSS check to be completed before the start date and that this responsibility falls to the party representing the candidate
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
</dl>



  </div>
</div>





        </main>
